### API Documentation: 
URL: /gemini
Method: POST
Content-type: application/json
Body param:
{
    "product": product name,
    "startDate": trend analysis start date,
    "endDate": trend analysis end date,
    "videoCount": number of video to fetch,
    "commentCount": number of comment to fetch per video
}

Purpose: 
A centralised flow calling trend analysis, sentiment analysis, and firebase inventory data. 
Build a prompt to be sent to Gemini Agent. Retrieve response in text string. 
Concatenate all datapoint in HTTP response for easy retrieval on UI and data visualisation, including: 
    - User input parameter 
    - Trend analysis result
    - Sentiment analysis result
    - Gemini recommedation response


Output: 
{
    analysis {
        input {
            product: 
            startDate:
            endData: 
            videoCount:
            commentCount:
        }
        inventory {
            record {}
        }
        trend {
            trend {
                start_value:
                end_value:
                percentage_change:
                trend: 
            }
            timeline {
                object {
                    date:
                    timestamp:
                    values {
                        object {
                            query:
                            value: 
                            extracted value:
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        sentiment {
            summary {
                clearly_positive:
                clearly_negative:
                neutral:
                mixed:
            }
            chartData { 
                object {
                    label: 
                    value: 
                }
            }
            comments {
                object {
                    comment: 
                    sentiment_score: 
                    sentiment_magnitude:
                    sentiment: 
                }
            }
        }
    }
    recommendation {
        Gemini generated recommedation text
    }
}

